The article is a letter from Joseph R. Biden Jr. addressed to the Chairman (or Chairwoman) in accordance with section 1264 of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2018. The letter states that the purpose of the letter is to transmit the annual report on the legal and policy frameworks guiding the United States' use of military force and related national security operations. The letter also mentions that both the unclassified report and its classified annex are enclosed. The letter is signed by Joseph R. Biden Jr.